We've been digging through the archives! Over 37 photo albums spanning nearly five decades of CCAKD history are now available on our website — from the very first formation meeting in 1977 to community celebrations through the years.

Browse photos from folklore festivals, Chinese New Year potlucks, Christmas parties, Canada Week parades, charity balls, and so much more. These images capture the people and moments that built our community in Kingston.

**Head over to our [Gallery](/en/gallery) page to explore these precious memories.**

If you recognize anyone in the photos or have stories to share about these events, we'd love to hear from you! Reach out at [info@ccakd.ca](mailto:info@ccakd.ca).
